南里民眾戶外運動需求，辦理的林口文中三滯洪池活化工程〈第二期〉，已於8月15日完工，工程主軸為打造體健運動空間，提升在地生活品質，使滯洪池發揮防洪以外的附加價值，不僅增添優質的體健設施，更是談天、散步、休憩好去處。 水利局長宋德仁表示，湖南里是文中三滯洪池公園位於新北市戶數及人口數最多的行政區，位於林口文化二路二段和中華一路口的文中三滯洪池，於去年5月啟用「林口區文中三滯洪池活化工程〈續〉」後，所營造具休憩氛圍的公園環境廣受當地民眾喜愛。 今年2月經當地蔡議員淑君及湖南里里長反映後，水利局即著手設計建置，內容包含設置4區人","0hUrqxl9_7Cl1MASNvnhR1CnZXCTJ_bRleKDdbXg9vVGk2NUleJ2JGM29WVTliZE0DJWRBMmwAEWwzOU4Kd2VG","IMAGE","生活","5e4b95e577475352cac02590","Article","新聞news","\u002F","https:\u002F\u002Fdc6965dc97bd4c3aa11f2360e74a8380@sentry.line.dev\u002F4","https:\u002F\u002Ftoday.line.me\u002F","1454987169","XmTxv7Ea8HP2Pwk0sKJ1Mw4Ty6AJ2gMH","是","最新","啟用自動貼文功能","查看更多","預告片","傳送","登入","星期一","星期六","星期日","星期四","星期二","星期三","您可以在手機版LINE上對這篇文章留言。","請至手機版LINE中觀看此影片。","4月","8月","12月","2月","1月","7月","6月","3月","5月","11月","10月","9月","尚無記錄。","%d天前","%d個月前","%d週前"));</script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/runtime.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/pages/_countries/v2/article/_urlPath.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/node_modules/b5726ebc.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/node_modules/62307b94.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/node_modules/6bc4eb58.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/article.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/commons/ad26fc6e.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/Subscription.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/node_modules/commons.bc5d4836.js" defer></script><script src="https://today.line.me/dist/bc5d4836/app.bc5d4836.js" defer></script>
